    "html_format": "<div class=\"document-view-wrapper\">\n<style>\n.html-preview * {font-family: Times New Roman; font-size: 12pt;}\n.html-preview a.NoteRef {text-decoration: none;}\n.html-preview table td {vertical-align: top;}\n.html-preview table {width: 100%;}\n.html-preview p {white-space: pre-wrap;}\n.html-preview .leading {width: 4px; display: inline-block;}\n.html-preview hr {height: 1px; padding: 0; margin: 1em 0; border: 0; border-top: 1px solid #CCC;}\n.html-preview .Normal {className: Normal; margin-bottom: 10pt;}\n.html-preview .a {font-family: 'Calibri';}\n.html-preview .Text {font-family: 'AntiquaUz'; font-size: 12pt;}\n</style>\n<div class=\"html-preview\">\n<style>.html-preview{width: 762px}</style><style>.html-preview{margin-top: 76px}</style><style>.html-preview{margin-bottom: 32px}</style><style>.html-preview{padding-left: 81px}</style><style>.html-preview{padding-right: 57px}</style><p style=\"text-align: center; margin-top: 5.65pt; margin-bottom: 5.65pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold;\">Т<span class=\"leading\"></span>А Қ И Қ </span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt; font-style: italic;\">(ипотека шартномаси бўйича)</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">Ўзбекистон Республикаси, </span><span class=\"structures structure-2\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#2}Шартнома тузилган нотариал округ номи</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span class=\"structures structure-3\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#3}Шартнома тузилган сана</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: 45.6px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">Мен –</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt; color: #ff0000;\"> </span><span class=\"structures structure-8\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#8}Шартномани тасдиқлаган нотариал идора жойлашган манзил</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">даги </span><span class=\"structures structure-9\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#9}Шартномани тасдиқлаган нотариал идора</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\"> нотариал идора нотариуси</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt; color: #ff0000;\"> </span><span class=\"structures structure-10\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#10}Шартномани тасдиқлаган нотариуснинг Ф.И.О.</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\"> </span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">Ўзбекистон Республикаси «Нотариат тўғрисида»ги қонунининг 64-моддасига асосан, </span><span class=\"structures structure-12\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#12}Ипотека шартномаси тузилган сана </span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\"> куни </span><span class=\"structures structure-13\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#13}Ипотека шартномасининг реестр рақами</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\"> реестр рақами билан қайд қилинган ипотека шартномаси бўйича гаровга қўйилган, </span><span class=\"structures structure-14\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#14}Гаровга қўювчининг яшаш манзили</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">-манзилда яшовчи </span><span class=\"structures structure-15\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#15}Гаровга қўювчининг Ф.И.О.</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">га тегишли бўлган </span><span class=\"structures structure-16\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#16}Гаровга қўйилган мол-мулкнинг манзили</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">-уй-жойга кредит шартномасидаги мажбуриятлар тўлиқ бажарилмагунга қадар бошқа шахсга ўтказилишини тақиқлайман.</span></p>\n<p class=\"Text\" style=\" text-align: justify;\"></p>\n<p class=\"Text\" style=\" text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">Реестрга </span><span class=\"structures structure-4\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#4}Ишончноманинг реестр рақами</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">-сон билан қайд қилинди.</span></p>\n<p class=\"Text\" style=\" text-align: justify;\"></p>\n<p class=\"Text\" style=\" text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">Давлат божи: </span><span class=\"structures structure-5\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#5}Ундириладиган давлат божи миқдори</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\"> сўм ундирилди.</span></p>\n<p class=\"Text\" style=\" text-align: justify;\"></p>\n<p class=\"Text\" style=\" text-align: justify; text-indent: 30.266666666667px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">Ҳуқуқий ва техник тусдаги қўшимча ҳаракатлар учун ундириладиган тўловлар: </span><span class=\"structures structure-6\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#6}Ҳуқуқий ва техник тусдаги қўшимча ҳаракатлар учун ундириладиган тўловлар миқдори</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\"> сўм ундирилди.</span></p>\n<p class=\"Text\" style=\"\"></p>\n<p class=\"Text\" style=\"\"></p>\n<p class=\"Text\" style=\"\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">Нотариус ________</span><span class=\"tab\" style=\"width: 47.2px; display: inline-block\"></span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\"> <span class=\"leading\"></span>_____________</span><span class=\"tab\" style=\"width: 47.2px; display: inline-block\"></span><span class=\"tab\" style=\"width: 47.2px; display: inline-block\"></span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\"> </span></p>\n<p class=\"Text\" style=\"\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\"> <span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span></span></p>\n<p class=\"Text\" style=\"\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\"> <span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span>М.Ў.</span></p>\n<p class=\"Text\" style=\"\"></p>\n<p></p>\n<p style=\"text-indent: 37.8px;\"></p>\n</div></div>",
